;  As a default, a person expected to work 1575 hours per year, not more.
;  - If you divide this by 12 (months), the resulting average monthly working hours are 131,25.
;  at 8 hrs / day = 16.40625 days per month
;  at 7.5 hours / day = 17.5 days per month
Do method $HoursInWorkDay Returns lnHoursPerDay
Calculate lnDaysInPersonMonth as 1575/12/lnHoursPerDay     ;; 1575 hours per year, 12 months per year, 60 minutes per hour = 7875
Quit method lnDaysInPersonMonth